sentences.english: Moni tor work quality and feedback abnormality to WT engineer.
sentences.chinese: 监督工作质量并及时向工程师反馈异常。

sentences.english: The feedback will become so strong it destroys the wormhole.
sentences.chinese: 反馈变得很强大而毁坏了虫洞。

sentences.english: In most cases the interviewer will give you feedback on the test.
sentences.chinese: 在大多数情况下，该面试官会给你测试反馈信息。

sentences.english: They didn’t call the PO after the demo to check his feedback.
sentences.chinese: 他们在演示后甚至不会去给PO打电话了解反馈。

sentences.english: And these various feedback mechanisms quickly facilitate jumpstarting the necessary people into action.
sentences.chinese: 这些反馈机制能够及时协助有关人员迅速采取行动。

sentences.english: The feedback you get will be extremely valuable.
sentences.chinese: 您将得到非常有价值的信息反馈。

sentences.english: A system of handwritten Chinese characters recognition based on feedback structure is constructed.
sentences.chinese: 构建一种基于反馈结构的手写体汉字识别系统。

sentences.english: Today, we got our progress reports.
sentences.chinese: 今天，我们收到了反馈表。

sentences.english: And just below, there was a toll free number to call with disputes.
sentences.chinese: 就在那行字下面，有个反馈异议的免费号码。

sentences.english: At the end of each wingbeat, the controller schedules the desired angle of attack according to state feedback errors.
sentences.chinese: 在每个拍动周期结束后，根据状态反馈误差调整迎角。

sentences.english: And that means they had to get feedback.
sentences.chinese: 这也就意味着他们必须得到反馈。

sentences.english: Multi-layer feedback BP network is a non-linear dynamic system.
sentences.chinese: 多层反馈BP网络是一种非线性动力学系统。

sentences.english: The principle of cross-layer feedback mechanism is presented and summarized here.
sentences.chinese: 对跨层反馈机制的原理进行了详细的阐述和总结。

sentences.english: Single Supply, Low-Power, High Output, Current Feedback Amplifier.
sentences.chinese: 单电源，低功耗，高输出电流反馈放大器。

sentences.english: This gives control back to the application.
sentences.chinese: 这可以对应用程序进行反馈控制。
